======
RULES
======


(portal)
[ > Player1 | GateIn ][GateOut|No Wall] -> [|GateIn][GateOut|Player2]
[ > Player2 | GateOut ][GateIn|No Wall] -> [|GateOut][GateIn|Player1]


( close gatein)
[ Action Player1|WallWeak][GateIn ] -> [ Player1|WallWeak][WallWeak ]
[ Action Player1|][GateIn ] -> [ Player1|][WallWeak ]
[ Action Player1 | WallWeak ] -> [ Player1 | GateIn ]

( close gateout)
[ Action Player2|WallWeak][GateOut ] -> [ Player2|WallWeak][WallWeak ]
[ Action Player2|][GateOut ] -> [ Player2|][WallWeak ]
[ Action Player2 | WallWeak ] -> [ Player2 | GateOut ]



